vious form it just was not working well. There are three main issues, which I am currently\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Daggers High&quot;","img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":568,"url":"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/2018\/07\/new-essay-mechanic\/","url_meta":{"origin":618,"position":3},"title":"New Essay Mechanic","date":"July 26, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Hey everyone! Just wanted to share with you the new Essay cards. The way the mechanic works has been changed a bit. Now, all players begin the game with 2 Essays and put them face down in front of them. At the end of the game, all players get the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Daggers High&quot;","img":{"alt_text":"","src":"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Writers-block.png?fit=857%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200","width":350,"height":200},"classes":[]},{"id":1692,"url":"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/2019\/05\/rulebook-preview-6-conspirator-spellslingers-techlandia-raid-boss\/","url_meta":{"origin":618,"position":4},"title":"Rulebook Preview 6: Conspirator, Spellslingers, Techlandia, Raid Boss","date":"May 18, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Hey everyone! Today I am back with another installment of my Rulebook Preview series. In this series, I take a look at tabletop games that have not yet been released or have been very recently released. I have not played these games, but simply reviewed the rulebooks (hence Rulebook Preview).\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Reviews&quot;","img":{"alt_text":"","src":"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/rulebook-preview-6.png?fit=601%2C600&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200","width":350,"height":200},"classes":[]},{"id":804,"url":"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/2018\/08\/achievement-rework\/","url_meta":{"origin":618,"position":5},"title":"Achievement Rework","date":"August 25, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Hey everyone! I changed the achievement cards just a couple of weeks ago,